snippet.title: BK: OSRS Announcement(Concept Download)
snippet.description:
Get excited. Planning for this sweet idea will be beginning soon. No details as I do not wish to fail on keeping any promises. The Bean Room will unfortunately have to be included now regardless of what anyone says though.

Here's the Patch if you want to mess around on this model: https://www.mediafire.com/file/mr4xke0ooilba50/Lumbridge.xdelta/file

The collectibles I put in are merely for show but you can go about collecting stuff like you would in a standard BK level. Just remember, the reward is the journey not the destination.

A Banjo-Kazooie rom is required to play this. Patch Banjo-Kazooie with this patch using an online patcher or your own if you have one. The resulting file will be this game in all of its conceptual glory.

Thanks. Have a nice day!
